snippet.title: Ja'afar's Nightmare official trailer
snippet.description:
Ja'afar is a little kid who's been through an accident lately ... a car accident ... he survived with all his family members for sure but the accident affected him and for the first time of his life he experiences a weird but unique nightmare ... you have to reach the end of this nightmare.

link to play the game:
https://thezwander.itch.io/jaafars-nightmare
